    dc:description "Figure 13. Agrostis elliottiana A whole plant B ligular area C spikelet D floret, abaxial view F floret, adaxial view. Based on Lehto et al. 10924 (ASU). Scale bars: 3 cm (A); 5 mm (B); 0.5 mm (C); 0.3 mm (D, E)." ;
